   Bush: In that sweep of the hotel? No. Apparently not.
   Q: Can you explain what elements of U.S. troops were involved?
Were they sent down _
   Bush: Special operations forces.
   Q: Were they sent from Ft. Bragg?
   Bush: There were _ I can't _ I'll leave others to tell you about
where they came from, but they were our special operations. And
when you have _
   Q: Does the army have a base there?
   Bush: No _ that I sent down there. And when you see Americans
